{"tid":1828129,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[真•Condom]  梵中協議關鍵主教郭希錦 遭北京迫害露宿街頭","createTime":"2020-01-17T13:58:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-17T14:13:22.000Z","uid":236171,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6d7216ab51dcb096a33fce3a8ca4da11e6363a2e","tid":1828129,"uid":236171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T13:58:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>梵中協議關鍵主教郭希錦 <br />\n遭北京迫害露宿街頭</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/amp/news/acn/202001170038.aspx?__twitter_impression=true\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Famp%2Fnews%2Facn%2F202001170038.aspx%3F__twitter_impression%3Dtrue&d=qHKTGL1WilUkyN31MLoEKOUDsY8FkShsNjUL6uXjEIs%3D&h=9a097e54\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/amp/news/acn/202001170038.aspx?__twitter_impression=true</a><br />\n最後更新：2020/01/17 10:40<br />\n<br />\n郭希錦原是教廷正式選派的福建閩東教區正權主教，2018年教廷和中華人民共和國簽署協議時，向中國讓步，要求郭希錦讓位給身兼政治協商會議委員的中國天主教愛國會前副主席詹思祿。<br />\n<br />\n郭希錦遭降級後未獲中國承認，反受到更嚴厲迫害。 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">郭希錦昨天接獲驅逐令，被迫離開主教府。政府甚至立刻「斷水斷電」，迫使他們遷出。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n信徒指中共政府以「違反消防安全」為由，迫害不願加入愛國教會的神父。有教會俾關閉，詹思祿任命愛國會神父接手後，教堂不經整修，立刻開放。<br />\n<br />\n閩東教區57位神父中至少有20人仍拒絕簽署加入愛國會。登記入會將使神父成為「黨的官員」，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">必須同意不向18歲以下的兒童和少年傳福音，也要在傳福音時主動宣傳至高無上的共產黨</span></strong>，這些都不符合天主教教義與精神。"},{"pid":"78149138c2dfd02908a3a8ddf62ae347e7f72b69","tid":1828129,"uid":155818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T14:00:08.000Z","msg":"梵蒂岡?<br />\n睇唔到睇唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73bef8efcd2c3c49400360f12cce78cf0cf5ae1f","tid":1828129,"uid":236171,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T14:00:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eW2ig9M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeW2ig9M.jpg&h=f983da2f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2c2e61d